code and continues the process.\"},{\"_id\":\"OS_Auth_CheckActivationNode\",\"name\":\"OneSpan Auth Check Activation\",\"collection\":true,\"tags\":[\"OneSpan\",\"multi-factor authentication\",\"marketplace\",\"trustnetwork\"],\"metadata\":{\"tags\":[\"OneSpan\",\"multi-factor authentication\",\"marketplace\",\"trustnetwork\"]},\"help\":\"Checks the status of a pending activation.\"},{\"_id\":\"OS_Auth_CheckSessionStatusNode\",\"name\":\"OneSpan Auth Check Session Status\",\"collection\":true,\"tags\":[\"OneSpan\",\"multi-factor authentication\",\"marketplace\",\"trustnetwork\"],\"metadata\":{\"tags\":[\"OneSpan\",\"multi-factor authentication\",\"marketplace\",\"trustnetwork\"]},\"help\":\"Checks the status of a request session.\"},{\"_id\":\"OS_Auth_GenerateChallengeNode\",\"name\":\"OneSpan Auth Generate Challenge\",\"collection\":true,\"tags\":[\"OneSpan\",\"multi-factor authentication\",\"marketplace\",\"trustnetwork\"],\"metadata\":{\"tags\":[\"OneSpan\",\"multi-factor authentication\",\"marketplace\",\"trustnetwork\"]},\"help\":\"Generates a random challenge which will later be presented to the user.\"},{\"_id\":\"OS_Auth_GetUserAuthenticatorNode\",\"name\":\"OneSpan Get User Authenticator\",\"collection\":true,\"tags\":[\"OneSpan\",\"multi-factor authentication\",\"marketplace\",\"trustnetwork\"],\"metadata\":{\"tags\":[\"OneSpan\",\"multi-factor authentication\",\"marketplace\",\"trustnetwork\"]},\"help\":\"Retrieve the authenticator list of the user.\"},{\"_id\":\"OS_Auth_UserLoginNode\",\"name\":\"OneSpan Auth User Login\",\"collection\":true,\"tags\":[\"OneSpan\",\"multi-factor authentication\",\"marketplace\",\"trustnetwork\"],\"metadata\":{\"tags\":[\"OneSpan\",\"multi-factor authentication\",\"marketplace\",\"trustnetwork\"]},\"help\":\"User login component for both IAA and OCA use cases.\"},{\"_id\":\"OS_Auth_UserRegisterNode\",\"name\":\"OneSpan Auth User Register\",\"collection\":true,\"tags\":[\"OneSpan\",\"multi-factor authentication\",\"marketpl